                            <comment id="86413" author="simmonsja" created="Thu, 12 Jun 2014 12:13:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch was merged upstream in commit  3ea8f3bcabe422c6b5778089ae0929c1028e58f8. This ticket can be closed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="74046" author="dmiter" created="Mon, 23 Dec 2013 20:26:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The same issue as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3486&quot; title=&quot;LBUG when exporting Lustre 2.4 via NFS on SLES11SP2: ll_dops_init: ASSERTION( de-&amp;gt;d_op == &amp;amp;ll_d_ops ) failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3486&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3486&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. The fix should be back ported to upstream.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
