                            <comment id="73878" author="rfehren" created="Thu, 19 Dec 2013 20:07:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just saw that this is already fixed in master and b2_5 with 6784a15c6ee32019237151a63755103c68ff51dd.&lt;br/&gt;
I tested the mainline client with this patch and it seems to work (stress tested for 30min. without error).&lt;br/&gt;
Please update b2_4 and mainline client with this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
